name: Corporal Rushing
Lore: 'Royal Naboo security officer in charge of protecting Amidala''s Throne Room. His wife and children were captured when the Trade Federation invaded the planet.',
Text: 'Deploys -1 to Naboo. While firing a blaster, adds one to total weapon destiny. Once per battle, if a battle droid was just hit by a blaster here, battle droid is lost and oppopnent loses 1 Force.',
